✨☀️ over the moon today, so happy I picked running back up. This time last year I heard them start the marathon from my apartment and told myself that will be me next year. Although I’m not running the marathon this year, I did complete the 5K with a PB of 27:33. I am going to continue my training and I have signed up for the half marathon in October. I’m hopeful to eventually run the full marathon this time next year (26 miles), but I am beyond pleased with the progress I have made.

Thank you so much to my friend Diamond @_thepsouknali who came out and supported me (I mean that sign, I cried ❤️) and my parents who I called immediately after crossing the finish line. 

Excited to see what comes next #running #5k #flyingpig #runrunrun #runningmotivation #runningday #flyingpigmarathon

5/29 - Hunger Run 5K ✨❤️ another fun fun fun day! Filled with friends new and old, with perfect weather. Felt a little congested still from being sick this month, but knees and shins were both in good spirits. 

Ended the race with a new PB 25:55 ✨

Finished it off with coffee @lolascoffeedowntown and @tasteofcincinnati @mamaafriquenc and my first alcoholic bev in a month! (Next month maybe I’ll treat myself to the next one!)
RICE it is #running #runningmotivation #runningreels

What Was I Saying podcast I’ve been working on premiers tomorrow and I’m really excited to share it with everyone ❤️💕💞 #podcast #running #runningmotovation #selfimprovement #runningpodcast

First Half Marathon!!! ✨✨🤌🏻 training for one in October, so I wanted to do a practice before the official so I could compare the two times. 

I packed 1 collas able water bottle, 3 gu gels, and stashed one water bottle to grab towards the end of my run. 

I was aiming for a pace of 9:50-10:00 a mile but kept it around 10:30. 

Afterwards got some chipotle and now I’m laying down and editing a podcast for you all ✨💕✨
